abstract="In this work we construct a new and highly efficient multilinear polynomial commitment scheme (MLPCS) over binary fields, which we call Blaze. Polynomial commitment schemes allow a server to commit to a large polynomial and later decommit to its evaluations. Such schemes have emerged as a key component in recent efficient SNARK constructions.",
